posts.post_content:
Breaking up a half-hearted attempt at the T205 Pirates ... the 35 cards below are available.

Post on the thread, PM me or email me at [url]mikefrohme@yahoo.com[/url] if you're interested.  I'll go by order received as best I can, and tie-breaker goes to email if its too close to call.  Prices assume Paypal (money owed/Gift) and include shipping - insurance is negotiable.  

Preference given to anyone wanting to keep a chunk of cards (player or back) together ... like Gibson ... :D (they mostly came in together)
